Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:40.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,10 anos atrás, no East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.06,0:02:44.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,havia um pequeno\Nvilarejo chamado Fuusha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:48.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Além do lugar onde seus\Nmoradores vivem em paz,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:52.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,está o Monte Colubo, onde o povo\Nraramente ousa pôr os pés.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:03:00.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Lá, apenas os fortes sobrevivem,\Ne os fracos estão fadados à morte.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:06.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Tô falando, vovô...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:08.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu serei o Rei dos Piratas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Chega dessa besteira de pirata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Me solta, pô!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:16.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Já não bastou comer aquela Akuma no Mi,\Nainda me vem com essa asneira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:22.05,Captions,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fad(500,0)\fnFOT-Greco Std B\b1\fs50\pos(641,717)\3c&H272A2E&\c&H272A2E&\1a&HFF&\t(455,500,\1a&H00&)}Monkey D. Garp\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N{\fnRoboto\fs45}(10 Anos Atrás)
